   BORDEN CHEMICALS &amp; PLASTICS L.P. (Columbus, Ohio) --
Joseph M. Saggese, an executive vice president of Borden
Inc., was elected chairman, president, chief executive
officer and a director of this partnership, succeeding
Anthony S. D'Amato, who was recently named president and
chief operating officer of Borden Inc. The partnership was
established in 1987 to acquire and operate Borden Inc.'s
basic chemicals and polyvinyl chloride resins business in
Geismar, La., and Illiopolis, Ill. Borden Inc. owns a 2%
interest and serves as general partner.
